The error shows that the export is failing because the path used to build the export archive has run out of space. 
 
Can you check your gitlab.rb file for the below setting? If this is a multi-node deployment, check the node(s) that run Rails/Sidekiq.
 
 Verify the configured shared path is mounted and has free space.
 
gitlab_rails['shared_path'] = '/var/opt/gitlab/gitlab-rails/shared'
 
You should also check that you have sufficient space in /tmp as this is also used  during the export process.
 
